fields.name: 60 Minutes
fields.description:
60 Minutes is an American news magazine and television program broadcast on the CBS television network. Debuting in 1968, the program was created by Don Hewitt, who chose to set it apart from other news programs by using a unique style of reporter-centered investigation.

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/60_Minutes

https://www.youtube.com/user/60minutes
